message.content: "cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM". The paper deals with visual question answering (VQA) models, which involve computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, "cs.CV" and "cs.CL" are the most likely sub-categories, followed by "cs.AI" and "cs.LG" which are also relevant to machine learning and artificial intelligence. "cs.MM" is less likely but still possible as it covers multimedia and image processing.
